[The blog [es] ](http://futbolstreet.blogspot.com/2010/08/skate-en-el-parque-
urbano.html)for the Art and Culture Association of [San
Isidro](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/San_Isidro,_Santa_Cruz) in Bolivia shares
pictures of an initiative to encourage children from the street to engage in
urban sports, [skateboarding](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skateboarding)
specifically. The event also included a
[breakdancing](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Break_dance) workshop.

